{"tid":2255562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"愛爾蘭宣布再度全國「封城」","createTime":"2020-10-23T15:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T04:17:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad469a1f3355f280d28e7bdba3e9fb25e9d96e5","tid":2255562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:45:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556406-20201023.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556406-20201023.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=80873fbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556406-20201023.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e3af0fa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556406-20201023.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭再度全國「封城」，所有非生活必需零售店或提供個人服務店舖，必須關閉，餐館、咖啡館和酒吧只提供外賣。<br />\n<br />\n民眾活動被限制在居所5公里範圍內，預料「封城」持續6周，違規民眾可被處以最高500歐元罰款。<br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭每天派出2500多名警察，在全國130多個固定或移動檢查站，進行相關執法活動。<br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭近期新增病例連續9天過千例，目前累計確診54476宗。"},{"pid":"9004e3773c1fd5d090a7bc2c37b89c29af2c38b1","tid":2255562,"uid":36441,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:50:10.000Z","msg":"其實好on9 一開返啲人走曬去開p 又爆過 無限loop"},{"pid":"de795232c21b31fe06484ba9a91c58f5b9dd79bb","tid":2255562,"uid":33874,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"9004e3773c1fd5d090a7bc2c37b89c29af2c38b1","tid":2255562,"uid":36441,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:50:10.000Z","msg":"其實好on9 一開返啲人走曬去開p 又爆過 無限loop"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"Ireland<br />\n一係飲酒<br />\n一係淋雨<br />\n無其他野做"},{"pid":"9a50e601b88faf08f3f12f43da24c61b8371ba0a","tid":2255562,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"de795232c21b31fe06484ba9a91c58f5b9dd79bb","tid":2255562,"uid":33874,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":